Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠洲的黃玉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧命的藍銅礦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷嗚的柘榴石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請就出發位置
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰艦指揮交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解，准將
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧，我要給妳們打屁股了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升起！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵空母上出現乙HiME了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看，大家都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來從妳身邊奪走謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派出我方乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦後退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行對乙HiME的戰鬥防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了啊，遙姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子期待她放水也沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從決定成為乙HiME時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有選擇餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉，聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的工作是誘敵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別被准將的步調打亂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是條約機構軍的本隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是戰爭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將彼此重疊的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖進記憶深處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟昨天不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我就站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降臨而下的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔地包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我訴說著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「守護」的真正意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾度仰望 無限寬闊的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了 那一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法再回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱切地 強烈地 勇猛地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在沒有光芒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能感覺到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你能發現我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第25話 蒼天的少女\N現在這情況，要是再用上古風琴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就重現十二王戰爭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了不要這樣\N才進行奇襲的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看過妳耶，妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊，准將
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海拉德少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法違抗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要互相怨恨啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照我們獲得的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西應該無法單點攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以靠那麼近的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就靠妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:03:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…要求救援…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把學園還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要將給予干擾的\N敵方真祖破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且讓二三小姐復活\N勝負就出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是靈廟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭老太婆，別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒禮貌，誰是老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹叫老婆婆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好了，動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹真的不能沒有我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，害妳受苦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，只要是為了妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，也還挺好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝出現叛亂軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那裡才是真正目標啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多該換下一招了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放出奴獸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神核心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始高次物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹，快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乃五柱之二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“冰雪的銀水晶”夏樹·庫魯格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以學園長的權限請願
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請開啟通往真祖之路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位，我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經連藏都不藏了嗎？凪大公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會直接命中！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是我們的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色山谷？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個都好韌命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過愛莉卡好像\N還沒使出“青玉”的真正力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，這些交給我跟命處理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳去鎮上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽，等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要使出\N那個貴石的真正力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得跨過一道\N無論如何都得跨越的牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了得到打倒“漆黑的金剛石”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與古風琴的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及藍色星球的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈廟的封印解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK，準備攻城砲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁書庫撐得住的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下，差一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝填銀彈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照愛瑞斯的情報\N女武神的真祖是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是學園長的砲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是反擊的“朗”煙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝進市內吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙，是狼煙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來五柱與學生們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該都能取回舞鬥服的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新連結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法，纜線…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二發，充填完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢宮愛莉卡，現在回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，妳好慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“青玉”的力量還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳英勇地出場是不錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看妳好像沒什麼長進呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然是騙我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳以為那種做法可以得到人心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是過份的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們真的很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以為了得到妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出任何事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧，別再這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手？都到這一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會阻止戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹應該擊破女武神的真祖了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道打偏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個遜腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃完全不一樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然這麼跩…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME們，別再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被放逐的女王現在回來幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是什麼都不知道的王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算這樣\N我還知道一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是不能讓凪玩弄世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼妳們沒發現？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此\N我們乙HiME還是得服從主命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的頭腦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是當個道具的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不需要乙HiME了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得很會說了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，我重新迷上妳了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連巴和貞德們一起阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要妳多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我無法不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，演員到齊了\N轉移到最後階段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣系統會因超過負荷而立刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正下個真祖的素材
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上又可以生出一堆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除女武神系統所有安全裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推力240%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種作戰我沒聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然背叛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼擺脫真祖的支配呢？\N捲捲…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓千繪擺脫支配的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不瞞妳說，就是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳根本沒隱瞞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱麗葉妳閉嘴
