Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這虎捲人偶之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無用武之地啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這次作戰之前就解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微覺得還不錯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都背叛我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這所學園之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情都很順我的意耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法，把妳們都消滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
