Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒告訴千繪姊姊就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真卑鄙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME系統便會告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種亂七八糟的代理戰爭系統啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起分擔痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最想開戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是該敬愛的國民們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，要先從誰下手呢
