Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒猜錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要與主人直接接觸
