Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，真白女王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切交給妳們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是離太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認證又會遭到妨礙的
