Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這隻區區的小螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要得寸進尺了！
