Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳給我記住！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡·夢宮！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴，對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這要由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我親手…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有最後一招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到妳了…
