Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成為乙HiME了喔
