Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明以為見面之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多好多話要說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子…一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下定決心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以妳主人的身份命令妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是出自我自己的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所決定的事情！
