Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡成功了呢
