Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.48,0:21:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，我要去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古風琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
